rows.name: Ask to learn more about New LA.

rows.label: tev013301_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Moorehouse to tell you about himself.

rows.label: tev013301_MSG0001
rows.name: I'm afraid that I do not possess the answers you seek.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev013301_MSG0002
rows.name:
You should ask someone who's a more active member
of society.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev013301_MSG5001
rows.name:
People speak of colonizing this world, but I merely wish
to live my life in solitude.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev013301_MSG5002
rows.name:
You can find more fruitful ways to spend your time
than by speaking with me.[ST:wait ]
